{
  "stem": "15577.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You should know, it was all the-- always relatively to-- to something.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So, at the time when we knew already, and everybody knew that the time comes that Plaszow will be liquidated, we knew that we, in-- in best case, will be sent to Germany, to other camps.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And these were mostly camps where people, if they were not determinated physically, immediately, sent to ovens, to gas chambers [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So they were determinated by-- in a very short time-- by very hard work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Don't forget, it was already the last year of the war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So, then we heard that Schindler decide-- not 'decide'-- decided, and got the permission, to-- Ah!",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "In the moment when-- when Plaszow is liquidated, also his place will be liquidated, because his camp is-- is a part of Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So he decided to, to, to use another trick.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And he got the permission from capital of Germany, from Berlin, to move his factory from Krakow through Germany.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But in this time, he won't make any--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--pots and pans, but he will make out of it something ammunition.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That means, more important for the-- for the army and for the-- for the war effort.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was-- everything was called-- you have to, to, to contribute to the war effort of-- of Germany.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was the slogan.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he bribed-- again, he bribed where he had to bribe, and the right people, in the right places, in this right moment.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he got the permission to move his factory or to build a new factory in Sudeten, in today's Czechoslovakia-- uh, Czech.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But at that time it was German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, to go there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
